{"word":"G3811 - παιδεύω - paideúō - pahee-dyoo'-o - Chasten","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παιδεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>paideúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pahee-dyoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Chasten"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தண்டி, கற்பிக்கப்படு, போதிக்கப்படு, உபதேசி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to train"},{"paragraph":"2. to chastise"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3816 - παῖς - paîs - paheece/3816\">G3816</a>; to <i>train</i> up a child, that is, <i>educate</i>, or (by implication) <i>discipline</i> (by punishment): - chasten (-ise), instruct, learn, teach."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3807 - παιδαγωγός - paidagōgós - pahee-dag-o-gos'/3807\">G3807</a>, <a href=\"#/G3809 - παιδεία - paideía - pahee-di'-ah/3809\">G3809</a>, <a href=\"#/G3810 - παιδευτής - paideutḗs - pahee-dyoo-tace'/3810\">G3810</a>, <a href=\"#/G3811 - παιδεύω - paideúō - pahee-dyoo'-o/3811\">G3811</a>, <a href=\"#/G521 - ἀπαίδευτος - apaídeutos - ap-ah'-ee-dyoo-tos/521\">G521</a>"}]}